
[Sun 24Apr2016]. Android Studio rendering problems;
   [Source: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/18195807/android-studio-rendering-problems]
   1. Open AndroidManifest.xml
   2. Change:
      android:theme="@style/AppTheme"
      to something like:
        android:theme="@style/Theme.AppCompat.Light"
   3. Hit "refresh" button in the "Previev" tab.

